long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Watch YouTube trending videos from around the world

Useful for:

- Expat and want to follow what's happening in your country
- Learning a language 
- Interested in another culture
- Curious about what people around the world are watching

You are normally restricted to see your YouTube recommendations in the main YouTube page. This extension allows you to easily access trending videos from the country of your choice.
